Package unisystem2023

Class News

java.lang.Object
unisystem2023.News
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class News extends Object implements Serializable
The News class represents a news item with a theme and text. Instances of this class are Serializable and added to the Database upon instantiation.
